text: Luiz Felipe Agostin Outerelo (born 11 December 1991) is a Brazilian diver. He competed in the men's synchronized three metre springboard event at the 2016 Summer Olympics. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Brazilian male divers Category:Olympic divers of Brazil Category:Divers at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Rio de Janeiro (city)
